node.text:
We’ve added two new Scoped Carbine courses at Maughan Ranch in Mattawa, WA:
Sept 17-19 & Nov 5-7, 2021
With Eastern Washington's rural & scenic topography as a backdrop, students will go from engaging targets at CQB to maximum effective range of their weapon system.  Developing full-field situational awareness and addressing the variables of physical and mental duress, shooters will understand what it takes to master the fundamentals of marksmanship in a practical, real-world environment. Limited to 10 students per class—register now to save your spot!

@maughan.ranch @aarondossphotography @leupoldoptics @oakleystandardissue @proofresearch @hornadymfg

💪🏽💥Repost from @gladiator_six
•
I Learned Some Stuff
——
Dialing in the @leupoldoptics Mark 5 Tremor 3 reticle, on my @triarcsystems 13.9” rifle during @followthroughbuck scoped carbine class in Raton NM, on some 12” steel. This was a drill Buck had us run with unknown distances that we had to quickly calculate and engage multiple targets. I learned a ton with Buck during the 3 day class. If your looking to push the limits of your weapon system in various terrain and distances this is the class for you. 
———
- Rifle: @triarcsystems 13.9
- Optic: @leupoldoptics Mark 5 Tremor 3
- Suppressor- @surefiresuppressors RC2
- Bi-Pod @magpod 
- Eye Wear: @oakleystandardissue 
- Ear Pro: @walkersgsm Razors
- Hat: @gladiatorgunz Dad hat
- Magazine Basepad: @magpod 
———
📷: @chris.edens 
———
#gladiatorgunz #gladiatorgunztraininggroup #buckdoyle #oakleysi #pushingforward #followthroughconsulting #recce #beentheredonethat #leupoldoptics #scopedcarbine #elevation

We’ve added two new Scoped Carbine courses at Maughan Ranch in Mattawa, WA:
Sept 17-19 & Nov 5-7, 2021
With Eastern Washington's rural & scenic topography as a backdrop, students will go from engaging targets at CQB to maximum effective range of their weapon system.  Developing full-field situational awareness and addressing the variables of physical and mental duress, shooters will understand what it takes to master the fundamentals of marksmanship in a practical, real-world environment. Limited to 10 students per class—register now to save your spot!

@maughan.ranch @aarondossphotography @leupoldoptics @oakleystandardissue @proofresearch @hornadymfg
